1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:10,045
More than 1,300 deaths have been linked to Europe's latest heatwave, as countries face dangerous temperatures and pressure on hospitals.

2
00:00:09,995 --> 00:00:17,101
Public health experts are urging better warning systems, cooling centres and support for older people.

3
00:00:17,101 --> 00:00:23,446
The crisis shows how extreme heat is becoming a social problem, not only a weather event.

